SciMed Solutions is a locally owned software company based in downtown Durham. Since 1997, we have been developing software solutions for the medical, scientific, and academic communities, and our business continues to grow in all of those areas.

Why Were Here SciMed's mission is to craft software that frees our clients to do what they do best: advance cutting-edge technology, improve lives, and effect social change.

What We Care About At SciMed, we seek to balance three things: Making the world a better place through our work. Creating a satisfying, engaging work environment at SciMed. Maximizing the average value (per hour worked over the entire expected life of the project) that we bring to the client.

Regardless of talents, experience, or role, we place a lot of trust in each employee. To keep that trust, we expect the following: We expect introspection. We expect continual improvement. We expect frequent, open, and honest communication. We expect all employees to take responsibility for their work and their promises. We expect employees to limit work to 40 hours per week.

Not everything is cut and dry, so when we find ourselves faced with decisions that cant be made based on the principles above, we consider the following guidelines. While the items on the right have value, we place more value in the items on the left. Teamwork over solo rock stars Professionalism over casualness In-office availability over off-site work Hiring the right personnel over increasing company revenues Individual decision making over management hierarchy Individual intelligence and creativity over rigorous predefined protocols

Learn more at www.scimedsolutions.com.

Scenable is an online platform for connecting to, participating in and interacting with local communities. Through a web and mobile (android/iPhone) application, Scenable brings the businesses, places, events, news and other people that make up local communities (Scenes) into the palm of your hand while also providing a platform for interaction and local commerce to happen online.

For individuals, Scenable is the online/mobile way to check out what local communities are all about.

For communities, Scenable allows them to take control of their online presence so they can become Digital Destinations.
